msgctxt "Talk_00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh, are you here because you heard the\n"
"rumors about Romah, too?\n"
"\n"
"I heard that she has a special technique\n"
"that will make you feel <2.se_co>more relaxed\n"
"than you have ever felt in your life<3.re_co>.\n"
"<4.so>But nobody said the wait was going\n"
"to be this long! I feel like I'll never know\n"
"what relaxation is ever again!\n"
"<5.so><6.te_si>Grrrrr, I'm so annoyed...<7.te_si>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<8.so>Well? Are you just gonna stand there, or\n"
"are you getting in line?<9.ch>"
msgstr ""

