msgctxt "Talk_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>...<2.pa>You're lying...\n"
"\n"
"<3.pa>\n"
"<4.so>The desert's dry heat and all the sun\n"
"you've gotten has completely dried out\n"
"your skin!\n"
"Rumors say that part of Romah's special\n"
"skills will leave people feeling\n"
"moisturized to perfection!\n"
"I can't stand when people lie! Grrr...<5.pa>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<6.so>...<7.pa>Hrmph. <8.pa>OK,<9.pa> I'm fine now.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"If I get angry, I'll create wrinkles between\n"
"my eyebrows.\n"
"\n"
"<10.te_si><11.so>Don't make me angry!<12.te_si>"
msgstr ""

