msgctxt "Talk_02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Huh? Wait, did you already...\n"
"But why? How?!<2.pa>\n"
"\n"
"<3.so>I've been here forever—she's not taking\n"
"people in the order that they arrived!<4.pa>\n"
"\n"
"<5.so>Wait! I can't get angry... I won't\n"
"get angry...<6.pa>\n"
"\n"
"...<7.pa>\n"
"OK,<8.pa> I'm fine now.\n"
"\n"
"You know, your skin looks super shiny,\n"
"and you look like you haven't got a\n"
"worry in the world...\n"
"<9.so>Yeah, yeah. I should just patiently wait\n"
"my turn. <10.pa>It'll be worth it."
msgstr ""

